WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
narrator: cold start — a clean scratch directory on disk.

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:06.500
narrator: octravpn init writes a config.toml and the node wallet key.

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.400
narrator: ls confirms the on-disk layout the daemon expects.

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:11.700
narrator: keygen mints a second key for the operator bond wallet.

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:13.500
narrator: bond.key is now present beside the node key.

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:17.000
narrator: identity prints the public key the chain will recognise.
